&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;AI-Powered Analytics&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Market research&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;In-depth analysis, Predictive insights&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Learning curve, High costs&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Automated Marketing Tools&lt;/td&gt;
